== 製作 ==
2018年11月8日，在[[新加坡|新加坡]]舉行的[[Netflix|Netflix]]作品發佈會「See What's Next: Asia」上宣佈推出《[[環太平洋_(電影)|環太平洋]]》的動畫劇集，故事將擴展前兩部真人電影<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://anime.eiga.com/news/107440/|title=Netflixオリジナルアニメはグローバル融合の新次元に　「パシフィック・リム」など5作品発表|publisher=アニメハック|date=2018-11-09|accessdate=2021-02-02|language=ja|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207131737/https://anime.eiga.com/news/107440/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Hood|first=Cooper|url=https://screenrant.com/netflix-pacific-rim-altered-carbon-anime/|title=Netflix Announces Anime Pacific Rim Series & Altered Carbon Movie|publisher=[[Screen_Rant|Screen Rant]]|date=2018-11-07|access-date=2021-02-02|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310105219/https://screenrant.com/netflix-pacific-rim-altered-carbon-anime/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Schaefer|first=Sandy|url=https://screenrant.com/pacific-rim-anime-netflix-seasons-premiere-date/|title=Netflix's Pacific Rim Anime Will Have 2 Seasons, Premiere In 2020|publisher=[[Screen_Rant|Screen Rant]]|date=2019-07-04|access-date=2021-02-02|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320054803/https://screenrant.com/pacific-rim-anime-netflix-seasons-premiere-date/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019年7月4日，[[傳奇影業|傳奇影業]]在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]][[Anime_Expo|Anime Expo]]中，宣佈該劇由傳奇影業和{{le|Polygon Pictures|Polygon Pictures}}共同製作，並將於2020年播出，初步計劃推出兩季<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2019/07/04/netflixs-pacific-rim-anime-is-coming-in-2020-confirmed-for-two-seasons|title=Netflix's Pacific Rim Anime Is Coming in 2020, Confirmed for Two Seasons|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2019-07-04|accessdate=2021-02-02|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320054718/https://www.ign.com/articles/2019/07/04/netflixs-pacific-rim-anime-is-coming-in-2020-confirmed-for-two-seasons|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年10月27日，在[[東京|東京]]舉行的「Netflix Anime Festival 2020」上宣佈正式劇名為《Pacific Rim: The Black》（{{lang|ja|パシフィック・リム: 暗黒の大陸}}），並釋出最新消息以及透露劇集將於2021年在Netflix全球首播<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cinematoday.jp/news/N0119474|title=『パシフィック・リム』Netflixアニメ版、2021年春に配信決定！|publisher=シネマトゥデイ|date=2020-10-27|accessdate=2021-02-02|language=ja|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207073143/https://www.cinematoday.jp/news/N0119474|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.polygon.com/2020/10/27/21535989/new-netflix-anime-resident-evil-pacific-rim-images|title=First look at Netflix’s Resident Evil and Pacific Rim anime, plus 5 newly revealed title|publisher=Polygon|date=2020-10-27|accessdate=2021-02-02|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308195131/https://www.polygon.com/2020/10/27/21535989/new-netflix-anime-resident-evil-pacific-rim-images|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

